metadata.name: Psycatdelics 2
metadata.description: Psycatdelics is a feline-fueled trip into the surreal, with each artwork whisking you away to a new world full of wonder and whimsy. All the cats put their claws into creating some truly meow-nificent pieces that are sure to have you feline good. Only 500 Psycatdelics will exist on the ethereum blockchain. These cats are also the key to everything catty by Imaginary Cat.
